{"tid":1295590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（分析）唔可以圍TVB","createTime":"2019-07-08T05:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T17:18:39.000Z","uid":195248,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f2aa2dc234e850ab6a13b85a9730b8b4f9cb5d","tid":1295590,"uid":195248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:27:07.000Z","msg":"TVB係人人得而誅之但係先睇利弊<br />\n我係將軍澳人好清楚將軍澳工業村係死胡同<br />\n<br />\n地勢方面:<br />\nTVB係工業村既深處  周圍都係山同海 冇人流冇大路可佔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XxHVsX5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXxHVsX5.jpg&h=1ea6981f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n交通方面:<br />\n主要交通係地鐵 而最近既地鐵站係康城站<br />\n發過咁多次夢都知be water一定要快閃<br />\n而康城站步行去TVB係要30分鐘!<br />\n重要既係睇返地鐵路線圖康城站由將軍澳站轉車<br />\n而每3班去寶琳先有1班去康城站<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bfjpmqc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbfjpmqc.jpg&h=37f9d34b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而由康城站上車要等10分鐘以上先會開車!<br />\n[red]即係由TVB走到返市區起碼要一個鐘頭![red]<br />\n<br />\n周邊環境:<br />\n工業村只有一堆工廠大廈  全部都起晒圍牆<br />\n[red]完全冇商場可以避狗[red]<br />\n唔好旨意蘋果可以開比大家入<br />\n到時只會困獸鬥<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3F1GoDm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3F1GoDm.jpg&h=07e2555a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VfuTZbM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVfuTZbM.jpg&h=3ed401ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTVB個位置係防守型堡壘  絕不適合圍攻"},{"pid":"56cd4eca6af3faf6f6c4141626faa431d3f66a6b","tid":1295590,"uid":195248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:28:34.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"aef236c097619c15afbe5b4a49d02f4c48b790e9","tid":1295590,"uid":268327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S4X6zGM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS4X6zGM.png&h=a721d437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人要團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似蟲蟲特工隊咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蟲蟲特攻隊 - 香港人Version<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295142\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295142</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫手推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96973ab22b1f8c258fa0e3163c118eb1dac4e94","tid":1295590,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:30:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幫手推上熱門<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［重要］區議會選舉招募各路人馬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295057\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295057</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n各位香港人，光復行動冇可能每日都做<br />\n好似屯門公園搞到今日咁烏煙瘴氣區議員責無旁貸<br />\n要清洗屯門公園始終要由根源做起<br />\n所以除左投立法會外<br />\n都請記得投票區議會踢走自動當選建制派<br />\n<br />\n唔好再俾建制派霸哂啲議席<br />\n就算唔係參選都可以做提名人，義工，助選團<br />\n行出第一步拒絕自動當選！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">總台TG：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/DistrictCouncil2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDistrictCouncil2019&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=849be12a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/DistrictCouncil2019</a><br />\n</span></span><br />\n登記左做選民既全部入group<br />\n急需大量提名人，義工助選團，Design等職位<br />\n入group後右下角Discuss入公頻搵各區admin<br />\n<br />\n要對抗黑警濫權一定要有議員抗衡<br />\n否則只會一直任人魚肉"},{"pid":"8e5cac59c85f195ad1ee70a55f769446449c757d","tid":1295590,"uid":176272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gST2j2t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgST2j2t.jpg&h=a98dbaa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TVe5hO9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTVe5hO9.jpg&h=722324b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PseQtVQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPseQtVQ.jpg&h=1b2c98b5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}